{
  "stem": "24958.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Goth told to the police, when we not going to find these girls, there-- there are going to be 50, or I don't know, people are going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the police did whatever they could, and they found these girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They found these girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought them back to the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had to come on the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was just the time that Schindler was there visiting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he hung these two girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the middle of the appellplatz, there was-- he hung-- he hung them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he shoot them yet, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Oskar saw that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He vomited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think-- that what my husband said, that he think from there on, he-- he changed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what he said later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- he started to work against them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, he had many conversations with Schindler, when he had-- many.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he gave-- there was a time where everybody had to give whatever little money they had yet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had to give everything away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler gave him at this time 500 zlotys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which was so much there then here $500.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I think my husband, at this time, was the richest man in camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had many conversation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he-- that was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my son got back and forth, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then there was the time where my-- my-- my-- my brother-in-law's brother was a police chief, a Jewish police chief in Bochnia, which was a little town not far away from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Goth told to Henry that there's going to be an action, that he should send away the-- the child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put him in a truck which went to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They covered him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
